<H3> <TI>   Justice Minister Views Conference </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Justice Minister Views Conference </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AB3005223094 Lagos Radio Nigeria Network in English 2100 GMT 
