<H3> <TI>   Government Establishes Relations With United Arab Emirates </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Establishes Relations With United Arab Emirates </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AB3105153094 Abidjan FRATERNITE MATIN in French 31 May 94 p 
24 </F>

<F P=103> AB3105153094 </F>
<F P=104>  Abidjan FRATERNITE MATIN </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Governments of the United Arab Emirates and the 
Cote d'Ivoire, desirous to enhance friendship between their 
peoples and promote bilateral cooperation relations on the basis 
of the UN Charter, in particular, the principles of equality, 
mutual respect, national sovereignty, and noninterference in the 
domestic affairs of states, have decided to establish diplomatic 
relations at ambassadorial level as of 30 May 1994. 

</TEXT>

