  [Begin Moura recording] It was not easy to make the UN 
Security Council adopt a satisfactory resolution on Angola under 
the present circumstances. Some circles even tried to hide the 
information on the best and final offer the Angolan Government 
made to UNITA, as its contribution to the search for and speedy 
conclusion of a general cease-fire and peace agreement in 
