  [Text] The Mozambique National Resistance [Renamo] is 
preventing electoral registration teams from operating in two 
locations of Malema in Nampula Province. The MOZAMBIQUE 
INFORMATION AGENCY [AIM] reports that Renamo officials in (Leia) 
