their seniors in Maputo to allow the teams to register voters 
for the October elections. Aurelio das Neves, chairman of the 
National Elections Commission in Nampula Province, told AIM that 
if a solution is not reached locally, he could still contact the 
Renamo leadership in Maputo today for explanations. 

